				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ {B}_xT=200 $$\end{document}, we generally need about 800 time samples. But for low SNR (e.g., 0 dB or less), the number needed can be considerably larger (see Eq. 42).

