				\begin{document}$$ {\mathrm{DCS}}^{\alpha}\left(\tau \right)=\left|{\rho}_s^{\alpha}\left(\tau \right)\right|\frac{\mathrm{SNR}}{1+\mathrm{SNR}} $$\end{document}

where SNR≜Rs0/Rn˜0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
