				\begin{document}$$ \mathrm{SNR}\triangleq {R}_s(0)/{R}_{\tilde{n}}(0) $$\end{document} is the ratio of mean squared signal to mean squared noise, and ρsατ≜Rss∗ατ/Rss∗0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
