				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ CV\triangleq \frac{\sqrt{\operatorname{var}\left\{{\widehat{R}}_{\tilde{x}}^{\alpha}\left(\tau \right)\right\}}}{\left|\mathrm{mean}\left\{{\widehat{R}}_{\tilde{x}}^{\alpha}\left(\tau \right)\right\}\right|}<1/10 $$\end{document}

The CV can be shown [2, 5] to be approximated by41CV≅1BsT1DCSατ.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
