				\begin{document}$$ CV\cong \frac{1}{\sqrt{B_sT}}\left(\frac{1}{DCS^{\alpha}\left(\tau \right)}\right). $$\end{document}

Substituting Eq. 39 into Eq. 41 transforms the requirement in Eq. 40 intoCV≅1BsT1ρsατ1+SNRSNR<1/10\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
